tutorial.title: Unique Shadow Abilities
tutorial.content:
1. Each turn, Girimehkala inflicts a <color=#FF423F>Mark of Calamity</color> on 2 Phantom Thieves.
This effect lasts for 2 turns.
2. When a Phantom Thief or Shadow with Mark of Calamity deals damage with a skill, <color=#FF423F>Calamity's Descent</color> is activated.
Calamity's Descent: Deals multi-target damage based on the user's Attack and transfers a Mark of Calamity to the main target.
3. All Shadows' final damage (excluding that from Calamity's Descent) is decreased by 60%.
4. After taking damage from Calamity's Descent, damage taken is greatly increased.
This effect lasts for 1 turn.

tutorial.title: Unique Shadow Abilities
tutorial.content:
1. Each turn, Girimehkala inflicts a <color=#FF423F>Mark of Calamity</color> on 2 Phantom Thieves.
This effect lasts for 2 turns.
2. When a Phantom Thief or Shadow with Mark of Calamity deals damage with a skill, <color=#FF423F>Calamity's Descent</color> is activated.
Calamity's Descent: Deals multi-target damage based on the user's Attack and transfers a Mark of Calamity to the main target.
3. All Shadows' final damage (excluding that from Calamity's Descent) is decreased by 60%.
4. Mark of Calamity can stack up to 2 times.
At 2 Mark of Calamity stacks, both will be spent to turn Mark of Calamity into <color=#FF423F>Ruinous Calamity</color>, dealing severe damage.

tutorial.title: Unique Shadow Abilities
tutorial.content:
1. Each turn, Girimehkala inflicts a <color=#FF423F>Mark of Calamity</color> on 2 Phantom Thieves and 1 Shadow.
This effect lasts for 2 turns.
2. When a Phantom Thief or Shadow with Mark of Calamity deals damage with a skill, <color=#FF423F>Calamity's Descent</color> is activated 1 time.
Calamity's Descent: Deals multi-target damage based on the user's Attack and transfers a Mark of Calamity onto the main target.
3. All Shadows' final damage (excluding that from Calamity's Descent) is decreased by 60%.
4. When Girimehkala has a Mark of Calamity, its damage is permanently increased by 50% after attacking.
5. When Incubus has a Mark of Calamity, it heals all Shadows after attacking.
6. If Succubus has a Mark of Calamity, it will inflict <color=#FF423F>Dizzy</color> on 1 Phantom Thief after attacking.
7. If Oni has a Mark of Calamity, it greatly increases the damage of all Shadows after attacking.
